These instructions will get the website up and running on your local machine:

Clone the repository

git clone https://github.com/WEDE-part-1/urban-threads.git


Open the project folder on your computer.

Launch the site by opening index.html in any modern web browser (Chrome, Firefox, Edge, etc.).

Explore the pages using the navigation links in the header.

No external build tools are required â€“ all CSS and JavaScript are loaded locally.

